    category: "Repair Tips",
    date: "2026-05-05",
    readingTime: "7 min read",
  },
  {
    slug: "garbage-disposal-reset-button-explained",
    title: "Garbage Disposal Reset Button: Why It Works and When It Won't",
    excerpt: "30% of disposal calls resolve at the reset button. InSinkErator dominance, the jam-clear procedure, and the actual repair categories that need a tech.",
