    date: "2026-05-05",
    readingTime: "7 min read",
  },
  {
    slug: "sub-zero-replacement-vs-repair-decision",
    title: "Built-In Refrigerator Replacement: Why Sub-Zero Owners Should Repair, Not Replace",
    excerpt: "Sub-Zero 700-series 30+ year service life, custom-panel cabinet integration, $1,500-$2,500 repair vs $12K-$24K replace + cabinet rework. Total cost of ownership math.",
    category: "Brand-Specific",
    date: "2026-05-05",
    readingTime: "9 min read",
  },
  {
    slug: "commercial-ice-machine-sanitization-health-dept",
